channel.description:
Can Someone Give Me A Link To An Empty Client From Scratch? ICBF Looking On Forums Also Im Getting This Error On My Vista x64 PC...
Attached Please Help It Crashes Whenever I Play Plus I Need A Java x64 Version For Compiling Please
Whenever I Walk Around Anywhere It Just Crashes Or If I Bank Also I Tried Adding : -Xint, Into The File It Works But Dramatically Slows The Client Down...
Please I Need Some Help RSPS....
Please Explain It In A Way A Monkey Can Understand Because I Cant Stand Jibberish Lulz
Thanks So Much Any Help Appreciated... :D

item.title: Can Someone Give Me A Link To An Empty Client From Scratch?
item.dc:creator: @primadude Primadude
item.description:
@primadude wrote:

Install the 64-bit version of Java. If you already have done so, use this batch file code to run the client:

@echo off "C:/Program Files (x86)/Java/jre6/bin/java.exe" -Xmx500m -cp .; client pause
